                        <div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;<h3 class="sectionTitle"
                                                                                style="text-align: justify;">What
                            personal data do we collect about you and how do we use your personal data?</h3>
                        <div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div>
                        <h4 style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Influencers Panel Members</strong></h4>
                        <div style="text-align: justify;">When you agree to become a member of our influencers panel
