                        <p style="margin-left: 40px; text-align: justify;">(B)&nbsp;<strong>Contact data</strong> –
                            postal address, email address and telephone number.<br>&nbsp;</p>
                        <p style="margin-left: 40px; text-align: justify;">(C)&nbsp;<strong>Special categories of
